title: Static Analysis

android.permission.READ_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to read all of the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to send your data to other people.

android.permission.WRITE_CONTACTS.description: Allows an application to modify the contact (address) data stored on your phone. Malicious applications can use this to erase or modify your contact data.

android.permission.READ_PROFILE.info: read the user's personal profile data
android.permission.READ_PROFILE.description: Allows an application to read the user's personal profile data.

android.permission.CAMERA.description: Allows application to take pictures and videos with the camera. This allows the application to collect images that the camera is seeing at any time.

android.permission.INTERNET.description: Allows an application to create network sockets.

android.permission.WRITE_EXTERNAL_STORAG.description: Allows an application to write to the SD card.

android.permission.GET_ACCOUNTS.description: Allows an application to access the list of accounts known by the phone.

android.permission.GET_TASKS.description: Allows application to retrieve information about currently and recently running tasks. May allow malicious applications to discover private information about other applications.

android.permission.RECEIVE_BOOT_COMPLETE.description: Allows an application to start itself as soon as the system has finished booting. This can make it take longer to start the phone and allow the application to slow down the overall phone by always running.

android.permission.SYSTEM_ALERT_WINDOW.description: Allows an application to show system-alert windows. Malicious applications can take over the entire screen of the phone.

android.permission.ACCESS_NETWORK_STATE.description: Allows an application to view the status of all networks.

android.permission.READ_PHONE_STATE.description: Allows the application to access the phone features of the device. An application with this permission can determine the phone number and serial number of this phone, whether a call is active, the number that call is connected to and so on.

android.permission.WAKE_LOCK.description: Allows an application to prevent the phone from going to sleep.

com.bitstrips.imoji.permission.C2D_MESSA.description: Allows the application to receive push notifications.

com.google.android.c2dm.permission.RECEI.description: Permission for cloud to device messaging.

android.permission.READ_EXTERNAL_STORAGE.description: Allows an application to read from SD Card.

android.permission.VIBRATE.description: Allows the application to control the vibrator.

android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKA.info: Allows an application to request installing packages.
android.permission.REQUEST_INSTALL_PACKA.description: Malicious applications can use this to try and trick users into installing additional malicious packages.

manifest_analysis.title: Launch Mode of Activity (com.bitstrips.imoji.ui.activities.DeepLinkActivity) is not standard.
manifest_analysis.desc: An Activity should not be having the launch mode attribute set to "singleTask/singleInstance" as it becomes root Activity and it is possible for other applications to read the contents of the calling Intent. So it is required to use the "standard" launch mode attribute when sensitive information is included in an Intent.
manifest_analysis.name: Launch Mode of Activity is not standard.

"terms_changed_content_line1" : "• ഞങ്ങളുടെ സേവന വ്യവസ്ഥകളിൽ, Snap-ന്റെ സേവനങ്ങളുടെ ഭാഗമാണ് Bitmoji എന്ന് വിശദീകരിച്ചിട്ടുണ്ട്."

"terms_changed_content_line2" : "• ഞങ്ങളുടെ സ്വകാര്യതാ നയത്തിൽ, ഞങ്ങളുടെ മൂന്നാം കക്ഷി ഉള്ളടക്കവും സമഗ്രതാ സമ്പ്രദായങ്ങളും ഞങ്ങളുടെ സേവനങ്ങൾ നിങ്ങൾ ഉപയോഗിക്കുമ്പോൾ ശേഖരിക്കുകയും പങ്കിടുകയും ചെയ്യുന്ന വിവരങ്ങളും സംബന്ധിച്ച് വിശദീകരിച്ചിട്ടുണ്ട്. പരസ്യം ചെയ്യൽ ഉദ്ദേശ്യങ്ങൾക്കായും നിങ്ങളുടെ തിരഞ്ഞെടുക്കലുകൾക്കായും നിങ്ങളുടെ വിവരങ്ങൾ ഉപയോഗിക്കുകയും പങ്കിടുകയും ചെയ്യുന്നത് സംബന്ധിച്ച കൂടുതൽ വിവരങ്ങളും ഞങ്ങൾ നൽകിയിട്ടുണ്ട്."
"terms_changed_subtitle" : "ഞങ്ങളുടെ സേവന വ്യവസ്ഥകളും സ്വകാര്യതാ നയവും ഞങ്ങൾ അപ്ഡേറ്റ് ചെയ്തിരിക്കുന്നു."

"terms_changed_content_line1" : "• ನಮ್ಮ ಸೇವಾ ನಿಯಮಗಳಲ್ಲಿ, Bitmoji ಯು Snap ನ ಸೇವೆಗಳ ಭಾಗವಾಗಿದೆ ಎನ್ನುವುದನ್ನು ನಾವು ಸ್ಪಷ್ಟಪಡಿಸಿದ್ದೇವೆ."

"terms_changed_content_line2" : "• ನಮ್ಮ ಗೌಪ್ಯತಾ ನೀತಿಯಲ್ಲಿ, ನಮ್ಮ ತೃತೀಯ ಪಕ್ಷದ ಕಂಟೆಂಟ್ ಮತ್ತು ಒಳಗೊಳ್ಳುವ ಅಭ್ಯಾಸಗಳು ಹಾಗೂ ನಮ್ಮ ಸೇವೆಗಳನ್ನು ಬಳಸುವಾಗ ನಾವು ಸಂಗ್ರಹಿಸುವ ಮತ್ತು ಹಂಚಿಕೊಳ್ಳುವ ಮಾಹಿತಿಯುನ್ನು ನಾವು ಸ್ಪಷ್ಟಪಡಿಸಿದ್ದೇವೆ. ಜಾಹೀರಾತು ನೀಡುವಿಕೆ ಉದ್ದೇಶಕ್ಕೆ ನಿಮ್ಮ ಮಾಹಿತಿಯ ಬಳಕೆ ಮತ್ತು ಹಂಚಿಕೆ ಮತ್ತು ನಿಮ್ಮ ಆಯ್ಕೆಗಳು ಬಗ್ಗೆ ಹೆಚ್ಚಿನ ಮಾಹಿತಿಯನ್ನೂ ನಾವು ಒದಗಿಸಿದ್ದೇವೆ."

"terms_changed_content_intro" : "સેવાની શરતો અને ગોપનીયતા નીતિ 30 ઑક્ટોબર, 2019 થી અમલી છે. તમારા માટે અગત્યના હોઈ શકે તેવા ફેરફારોને સમજવા માટે કૃપા કરીને બંનેને વાંચો! અહીં મુખ્ય ફેરફારોનો સારાંશ આપેલો છે:"
"terms_changed_content_line1" : "• અમારી સેવાની શરતોમાં, અમે સ્પષ્ટ કર્યું છે કે Bitmoji એ Snap ની સેવાઓનો એક ભાગ છે."

"terms_changed_content_line2" : "• અમારી ગોપનીયતા નીતિમાં, અમે અમારી તૃતીય-પક્ષ સામગ્રી અને સંકલન પ્રથાઓ, તેમજ તમે અમારી સેવાઓનો ઉપયોગ કરો છો ત્યારે અમે જે માહિતી એકત્રિત અને શેર કરીએ છીએ તેને સ્પષ્ટ કરી છે. અમે જાહેરાત હેતુઓ અને તમારી પસંદગીઓ માટે તમારી માહિતીના ઉપયોગ અને શેરિંગ વિશે વધુ માહિતી પ્રદાન કરી છે."
"terms_changed_subtitle" : "અમે અમારી સેવાની શરતો અને ગોપનીયતા નીતિ અપડેટ કરી છે."

playstore_details.title: Bitmoji
playstore_details.description:
Bitmoji is your own personal emoji. 

• Create an expressive cartoon avatar 
• Choose from a huge library of stickers – all featuring YOU 
• Use Bitmoji in Snapchat and wherever else you chat 

Using Bitmoji in Snapchat unlocks Friendmoji – 2-person Bitmojis featuring you and your friends!
playstore_details.summary: Bitmoji is your personal emoji. Use it in Snapchat and wherever else you chat!
